COPS in Texas, USA, have discovered the beheaded body of a wife who had been married for less than four months. The woman’s husband was then charged for her horrific murder. The Post reports that the body of the 21-year-old was discovered at home, but her head was missing. “It was a portion of a body, dismembered, and a residence that was covered in blood; a gruesome scene at best,” cops said on Thursday, 12 January. You must be SIGNED IN to read comments The husband, Jared Dicus (21), confessed to the killing. A knife, believed to be the murder weapon, was found at the property with the woman’s severed head. She is believed to be have been dead since around 11pm the night before her remains were discovered.